---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer>
	<div class="footer-inner">
		<div>
			<strong>Lumynn</strong> - Private knowledge, grounded intelligence.<br />
			<span class="muted">First product of a family of tools for people who build things that last.</span>
		</div>
		<div class="links">
			<a href="https://github.com/huyu9711/lumynn" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>
			<a href="/blog">Notes</a>
			<a href="/about">About</a>
		</div>
		<div class="legal muted">
			© {year} Lumynn. Self-hosted. Your files. Your server.
		</div>
	</div>
</footer>

<style>
	footer {
		padding: 2.75rem 1.25rem 2rem;
		border-top: 1px solid var(--lumynn-border);
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		color: var(--lumynn-muted);
	}
	.footer-inner {
		max-width: 1080px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		display: flex;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		gap: 1.25rem 2.5rem;
		justify-content: space-between;
		align-items: flex-start;
	}
	.links {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1.1rem;
	}
	.links a {
		color: inherit;
		border-bottom: 1px solid transparent;
	}
	.links a:hover { border-bottom-color: var(--lumynn-border-strong); color: var(--lumynn-ink); }
	.legal {
		font-size: 0.78rem;
		margin-top: 0.35rem;
	}
	@media (max-width: 720px) {
		.footer-inner { flex-direction: column; gap: 0.9rem; }
	}
</style>
